[center]Infexis Source [img]http://i42.tinypic.com/f4cgy.png[/img]
Information: Welcome to Infexis Thread. Infexis is a RuneScape Private Server based off of the 317 protocol. Our goal is to provide you with a server that is fun to play, and minimal bugged with many features. Another thing we're working on is the combat, the combat is very important to be very focused.
About Us: We have been coding Infexis for a few months now and we starts to get to the end of this project. Our goal on Zanzito Project was to make a server minimal bugged but mostly things work ex, Skilling, Combat, Minigames... This Project is a succes and alost done. Once we finish it, its gonna get released out for the world.
